title: Grateful Dead Live at Silva Hall, Hult Center on 1983-08-29

description:

Shakedown Street, New Minglewood Blues,  Friend Of The Devil, Hell In A Bucket, Bird Song, It's All Over Now, Might As Well

Drums > Space > The Wheel > The Other One > Goin' Down The Road Feeling Bad >

U.S. Blues

Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
